title: Bloomberg Businessweek Weekend - May 18th, 2019
itunes:title: Bloomberg Businessweek Weekend - May 18th, 2019
description:
Hosted by Jason Kelly and Taylor Riggs

Featuring highlights from the latest issue of Bloomberg Businessweek.

-Sonali Basak details the Uber IPO blame game

-Ellen Huet shows how WeWork us turning to financial gymnastics to keep expanding

-Joe Mayes explains how Britain’s businesses have already lost, Brexit or no Brexit

-Planet Fitness CEO, Chris Rondeau, on the business of fitness centers

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
